title: Nvidia Intends to Price Newest AI Chips to Appeal to Wide Group of Users
description: CEO Jensen Huang says the company is positioned to capture a large share of new spending on data centers.

title: WuXi AppTec's Net Profit Jumps, Reiterates It Doesn't Pose Security Threat
description: Chinese biotechnology company WuXi AppTec said net profit jumped last year, while reiterating that it doesn’t pose a security threat to any country amid worries over a potential U.S. ban.
